---
description: Mandatory domain specialist routing for domain-critical logic
alwaysApply: false
globs:
  - "**/*.ts"
  - "**/*.tsx"
  - "**/*.js"
  - "**/*.jsx"
---

Use `domain-agent` whenever a task affects business-critical rules, financial calculations, repayment logic, penalties, schedules, ledger behavior, or audit-sensitive domain decisions.

When the domain agent is required by this scope and not consulted, the task must not be finalized as pass.
